'''= The mission of CSTART, the Collaborative Space Travel and Research Team, is to organize and finance the efforts of space enthusiasts around the world who are interested in using collaborative design, volunteer labor, innovative, low-cost technology and open data sharing to further the cause of manned and unmanned space exploration and research.''' [http://cstart.org/wiki/CSTART_Mission_Statement]

